1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
<i>Legend of Fei</i>

16
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:56,040
<i>Episode 45</i>

17
00:01:56,690 --> 00:01:58,330
When it’s dog-eat-dog between them,

18
00:01:58,330 --> 00:02:00,650
we can take advantage of it.

19
00:02:01,370 --> 00:02:02,220
That’s right.

20
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:05,180
First, Yu Wenzhi asked Pathetic Clam
to steal the tokens

21
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:07,260
then he told Shen Tianshu to rescue her.

22
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,690
With him in between,

23
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:11,140
those two will be suspicious
about each other

24
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,740
and won’t be of one mind.

25
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:15,000
Even if he’s delayed,

26
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,310
I can still make him

27
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,800
part of the game

28
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:20,040
to churn the waters

29
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,910
this time.

30
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,160
Are you saying...?

31
00:02:28,510 --> 00:02:29,230
Isn’t it...?

32
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,230
Yes.

33
00:02:30,230 --> 00:02:32,320
It belongs to Yu Wenzhi’s spy.

34
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:36,240
Since he’s colluding with Pathetic Clam,

35
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,520
I’ll use him

36
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,520
to drive a wedge

37
00:02:41,110 --> 00:02:44,110
between Pathetic Clam and Shen Tianshu.

38
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:45,910
If they’re against each other,

39
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:46,830
she won’t

40
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:48,910
hand over the tokens to Shen Tianshu.

41
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:52,550
With those tokens in hand,

42
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:53,750
who will she

43
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,830
side with?

44
00:02:57,110 --> 00:03:00,360
Aren’t those Demons

45
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,750
full of tricks and schemes?

46
00:03:02,270 --> 00:03:03,270
Very well.

47
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:05,440
It’s payback time!

48
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,190
Let Shen Tianshu be hoist

49
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,800
with his own petard.

50
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,240
Lord Gu,

51
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,520
bad news.

52
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,080
The bridge has been destroyed.

53
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,030
There are no boats around.

54
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:34,600
How should we cross the river?

55
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,910
It must’ve been done on purpose.

56
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,270
Correct.

57
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,630
You have to beat me first

58
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:58,440
to join Shen Tianshu.

59
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,750
Madam Nichang,

60
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,720
why are you here?

61
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,080
What’s it to do with you?

62
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,750
I’m asked

63
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:11,520
to stop you here.

64
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:21,750
You think you chicks

65
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:23,670
are my match?

66
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,100
Gu Tianxian.

67
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,470
Long time no see.

68
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:34,960
What about us, too?

69
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,000
Are we your match together?

70
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:19,000
Go, go, go.

71
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,600
Let’s go.

72
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,880
Mr. Li,

73
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,000
my men found

74
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,390
eyes and ears of Demons here.

75
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:38,720
Please follow me.

76
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:41,000
Be careful and keep a low profile.

77
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,070
Fei and Mr. Xie arrived here yesterday.

78
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,110
Did anyone see them?

79
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:45,550
A beggar

80
00:05:45,550 --> 00:05:47,670
saw a man and a woman earlier

81
00:05:47,670 --> 00:05:49,390
who carried a long blade.

82
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:52,200
That must be them.

83
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:53,950
Please tell them

84
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,440
to meet us here.

85
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:58,600
Fei was injured
by Pathetic Clam yesterday.

86
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,480
I wonder how she is now.

87
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,270
Alright. I’m on it.

88
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,760
<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

89
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,480
Madam Nichang.

90
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,720
Chief Xu,

91
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:42,230
did you also receive
a letter from Chuchu?

92
00:06:42,230 --> 00:06:43,350
No.

93
00:06:43,350 --> 00:06:44,230
It was Miss Zhou.

94
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:45,640
She asked me

95
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,790
to teach those bastards a lesson.

96
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,720
Luckily, I asked Madam Nichang for help.

97
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,920
Demons do have backups.

98
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:16,920
<i>Xiangdong Tavern</i>

99
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,760
Right after Lord Hu came back,

100
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,920
she argued with Lord Shen.

101
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,230
With those two together,

102
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:25,040
our chance of winning is slim.

103
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,920
Stop gossiping about her!

104
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,160
That’ll get you killed!

105
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,510
Let’s go.

106
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:36,600
<i>Xiangdong Tavern</i>

107
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,350
Have a seat, Miss.

108
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:41,880
Best wishes to you.

109
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,760
Says who?

110
00:07:51,230 --> 00:07:52,510
Miss Zhou,

111
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,790
I’m with the Route Gang.

112
00:07:54,790 --> 00:07:56,670
Mr. Li is waiting for you at the dock.

113
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:57,880
You can go join him.

114
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,880
Thanks.

115
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:10,440
You must be hungry.

116
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:12,760
Here.

117
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,830
Have some plum cakes.

118
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,480
That’ll help you remember things.

119
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:20,110
Why bother?

120
00:08:20,110 --> 00:08:22,000
Feed her my poison.

121
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,920
The excruciating pain

122
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,000
will certainly help jog her memory.

123
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:34,440
Don’t scare her.

124
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:38,480
She can take her time.

125
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:42,600
Let’s play a game.

126
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,320
You’re a carpenter, right?

127
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,000
You need your hands

128
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,390
to support your family, don’t you?

129
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,230
The game we’re playing

130
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:02,000
is called Chopping off Fingers.

131
00:09:03,590 --> 00:09:05,440
Here’s the rule.

132
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,910
On my count of three,

133
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:10,710
if you still don’t remember anything,

134
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:13,590
he’ll lose one finger.

135
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:17,520
Then I’ll count again.
If I still hear nothing,

136
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:20,520
he’ll lose one more.

137
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,520
Let’s see

138
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:24,320
how many fingers he’ll lose in total.

139
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:26,150
Let’s begin.

140
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:28,400
One.

141
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,710
No, no!

142
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,200
Two.

143
00:09:40,230 --> 00:09:41,400
Three.

144
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:44,550
Stop! I’ll tell you.

145
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:47,520
I’ll write it down.

146
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:57,200
Young lady,

147
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:59,640
here’s a friendly reminder.

148
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,790
I’ve been looking for that treasure

149
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,790
long before you had been born.

150
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:06,110
Don’t you

151
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:07,910
try to fool me.

152
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,880
Li Sheng.

153
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,590
There you are.

154
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:27,280
Are you alright?

155
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,400
I’m fine.

156
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:31,400
Pathetic Clam and Shen Tianshu
are together now.

157
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,640
I know.

158
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:35,470
We’ve checked around the town

159
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,840
and figured out where their people are.

160
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,080
It’s too risky

161
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,590
for us to act alone.

162
00:10:40,590 --> 00:10:43,760
The current situation is in favor of us.

163
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,280
I’ve thought up a plan

164
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,030
to cast in a bone between them.

165
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:51,080
Shen Tianshu is suspicious by nature.

166
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,200
He can’t tolerate any deception.

167
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:55,880
As his most trusted help,

168
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,960
Pathetic Clam is colluding
with Yu Wenzhi.

169
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,400
I’m sure she knows

170
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,960
Shen Tianshu is suspecting her.

171
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,640
She won’t

172
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,880
hand over those tokens easily.

173
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,320
They’re her biggest leverage.

174
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,760
So I bet they’re still on her.

175
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,000
That’s where we can come in

176
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,350
and drive a wedge

177
00:11:15,350 --> 00:11:16,590
between them

178
00:11:16,590 --> 00:11:19,110
to avoid battling Shen Tianshu head-on.

179
00:11:21,110 --> 00:11:22,880
It’s us against them, isn’t it?

180
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,000
Let’s do it!

181
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,520
Why are you making it complicated?

182
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,710
Pathetic Clam is crafty.

183
00:11:29,110 --> 00:11:31,550
Don’t leave her any wiggle room.

184
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:33,280
Beware of her.

185
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,320
You’re simple-minded.

186
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,670
Don’t hold us back.

187
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:37,440
Relax. I once battled her.

188
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,200
I’m aware of her tricks.

189
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,790
Alright.

190
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:44,080
Let’s split up.

191
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,150
If anything happens,

192
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:47,320
fire the whistling arrow

193
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,760
to alert each other.

194
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:51,960
Do not take risks.

195
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,110
Our enemies

196
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:53,910
are the top two

197
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,640
notorious Demons.

198
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,200
If you’re in danger,

199
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,280
or things go against you,

200
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,590
leave first.

201
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:00,880
We can abort the plan

202
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:02,150
and wait for another chance.

203
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:03,910
Yes, Madam.

204
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:10,400
Hang on.

205
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,230
You freaked me out.

206
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,710
Miss Zhou,

207
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:32,400
we still have resources here.

208
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,640
If you need anything,

209
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,400
don’t hesitate to tell me.

210
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,590
Sure. Thanks.

211
00:12:41,350 --> 00:12:42,910
What did you say to Li Sheng?

212
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:44,840
Nothing special

213
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,760
other than a contingency plan.

214
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,320
I guess Shen Tianshu

215
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,880
didn’t take too many people with him.

216
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,590
We can

217
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:55,670
bluff him with the Anping Army

218
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:58,110
if necessary.

219
00:12:58,590 --> 00:12:59,640
Let’s go.

220
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,000
Leave it to me.

221
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,760
I’ll lure him out.

222
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,440
Yang Jin,

223
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:13,000
you have to really sell it.

224
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,440
Don’t fall into

225
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,280
Pathetic Clam’s traps.

226
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,520
Got it.

227
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,670
And you stop Demons

228
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,110
with our men.

229
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,520
Good.

230
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:54,400
There you go.

231
00:13:56,230 --> 00:13:57,440
Why are you crying?

232
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:02,080
Could you let us go?

233
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:13,350
Would you like a plum cake?

234
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,710
Alright.

235
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:16,910
Your job is done.

236
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:18,760
We don’t need you anymore.

237
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,790
Not yet.

238
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:22,960
Tianshu,

239
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,760
she humiliated me

240
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,520
back in the Cloud Ravine.

241
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:28,640
I must kill her!

242
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,230
Be patient.

243
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:31,710
Once you’re done crying,

244
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:32,640
recite the poem

245
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:35,470
from the beginning.

246
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:37,030
Then I’ll consider

247
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:39,880
if I’ll release you.

248
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,670
Let Senior Master Li go first.

249
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,880
Sure.

250
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:54,960
Why would I

251
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,590
keep a carpenter?

252
00:14:56,590 --> 00:14:57,910
Tianshu,

253
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:59,440
you aren’t yourself today.

254
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,760
How could she lead you by the nose?

255
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,470
Tianying,

256
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:06,910
if she piled up a bunch of nonsense,

257
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:09,790
she couldn’t recite it accurately.

258
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,910
That’s why I’m asking her to do it.

259
00:15:11,910 --> 00:15:13,910
If one word doesn’t match,

260
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:18,110
I’ll kill the carpenter.

261
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,470
And she can

262
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,520
have a taste of your poison.

263
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,080
Begin.

264
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:46,230
This dough figure is you, isn’t it?

265
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:50,960
It’s quite accurate.

266
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:02,640
I’ll do it. I’ll do it. I’ll do it.

267
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:09,280
“I go to Wuzhou to see you

268
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:12,030
where mountains appear at dusk.

269
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,150
Climb... Climb...”

270
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:15,670
Climb the mountain to overlook
the north or the south?

271
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,880
“Climb the mountain to
overlook the north of the river.

272
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:20,910
Send stones and Ganoderma.

273
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:22,200
The... The...

274
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,670
The valley is beautiful

275
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:29,110
where birds sing beautifully.

276
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:33,760
Music comes everywhere

277
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:37,400
when four songs are played”.

278
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,670
All correct.

279
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:43,030
Good. Well done.

280
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:46,320
Senior Master Li.

281
00:16:47,590 --> 00:16:49,760
Senior Master Li, go.

282
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:50,670
Says who?

283
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:51,400
You...

284
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,840
Tianying,

285
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,960
let him go.

286
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:54,910
As seniors,

287
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:57,550
we shouldn’t lie to a girl.

288
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,350
Tianshu,

289
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:07,960
if you let him go, then what?

290
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:09,670
To alert his people?

291
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,790
People of the Fortress
of the Forty-Eight

292
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,760
could’ve followed me here.

293
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,790
It’s time to leave.

294
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,470
Tianying,

295
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,040
where are the five tokens?

296
00:17:27,350 --> 00:17:28,950
Tokens?

297
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,920
I risked my life to get them for you.

298
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,430
Do you know how dangerous it was?

299
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,680
Zhou Fei almost killed me!

300
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:42,430
Tianying,

301
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:44,950
that poem

302
00:17:44,950 --> 00:17:47,680
is the clue to finding the treasure.

303
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,800
We’re all set.

304
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:50,190
Give me the tokens

305
00:17:50,190 --> 00:17:52,470
and we’ll head to
the Big Medicine Valley

306
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:53,880
to get the Book of Almighty Medicine

307
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,800
to treat you.

308
00:17:59,190 --> 00:18:00,830
The Big Medicine Valley?

309
00:18:02,230 --> 00:18:03,350
Sure.

310
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:05,400
Only if you kill her first.

311
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:08,710
What’s wrong? You can’t do it?

312
00:18:09,430 --> 00:18:10,680
Tianying,

313
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:14,350
just ignore that girl.

314
00:18:15,470 --> 00:18:17,310
Fine. I’m off.

315
00:18:32,130 --> 00:18:33,210
Tianying,

316
00:18:33,210 --> 00:18:34,250
you...

317
00:18:43,210 --> 00:18:44,940
Do you still care about me?

318
00:18:46,610 --> 00:18:48,850
Why are you doing this?

319
00:18:49,610 --> 00:18:51,460
“Flowers will grow better next year.

320
00:18:52,090 --> 00:18:54,330
Who will enjoy them with me?”

321
00:18:54,330 --> 00:18:55,300
Tianshu,

322
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:56,420
am I already

323
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:58,970
a withered flower in your eyes?

324
00:18:58,970 --> 00:19:00,700
What makes you say that?

325
00:19:01,130 --> 00:19:03,490
I tolerated them for so long

326
00:19:03,490 --> 00:19:06,460
only to find
the Color of Ocean and Heaven for you.

327
00:19:06,730 --> 00:19:08,130
Tianying,

328
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:11,540
don’t argue with me about the tokens.

329
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:13,130
If it’s for me as you said,

330
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,940
does it matter

331
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:16,370
who keeps them?

332
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:18,490
Don’t you trust me?

333
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:21,300
Look at you.

334
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:23,490
Listen to yourself.

335
00:19:35,700 --> 00:19:37,460
Every street is under Demons’ watch.

336
00:19:37,460 --> 00:19:38,780
We must be careful.

337
00:19:40,090 --> 00:19:41,660
If... If you kill me,

338
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,970
my aunt will avenge my death.

339
00:19:43,970 --> 00:19:46,940
She’s poisoned.

340
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:48,780
Maybe she’s dead before you.

341
00:19:48,780 --> 00:19:50,130
Liar!

342
00:19:50,130 --> 00:19:52,210
That’s impossible!

343
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:54,580
What’s Yan doing here?

344
00:19:56,660 --> 00:19:59,540
So the girl Demons mentioned is...

345
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:01,610
is Yan!

346
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:06,420
I asked her

347
00:20:06,420 --> 00:20:07,900
to buy osmanthus liquor for you.

348
00:20:07,900 --> 00:20:09,010
I didn’t know...

349
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:12,730
Fei,

350
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:15,580
it’s my fault.

351
00:20:15,580 --> 00:20:16,970
She got caught

352
00:20:16,970 --> 00:20:18,850
because of me.

353
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:20,250
How about this?

354
00:20:20,250 --> 00:20:21,700
I’ll ask Shen Tianshu to take me

355
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:22,970
and let her go.

356
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:24,580
No!

357
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:27,300
Hear me out, Fei.

358
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,250
I’ll be his hostage

359
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:29,700
and get Li Yan out.

360
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:30,780
Then

361
00:20:31,090 --> 00:20:33,210
I’ll use Gu Tianxian
caught by the Route Gang

362
00:20:33,210 --> 00:20:34,490
to cut a deal with Shen Tianshu.

363
00:20:34,490 --> 00:20:35,900
That way, I can stall them

364
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:36,780
and

365
00:20:37,210 --> 00:20:38,900
make it easier for Li Sheng

366
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:40,970
to lure Pathetic Clam out.

367
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:42,610
But...

368
00:20:43,090 --> 00:20:45,090
Don’t worry.

369
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:46,820
Shen Tianshu is in debt to my father.

370
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:49,010
He won’t harm me for old times’ sake.

371
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:50,540
Besides,

372
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,820
I have questions for him about the past.

373
00:20:53,130 --> 00:20:55,700
All that will be enough to distract him.

374
00:20:56,490 --> 00:20:58,700
Alright. Once I get Li Yan

375
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,010
and take her back,

376
00:21:00,010 --> 00:21:01,730
I’ll wait for you outside.

377
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:02,850
Be very careful.

378
00:21:03,370 --> 00:21:04,460
If things go south,

379
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:06,130
I’ll pull you out immediately.

380
00:21:06,130 --> 00:21:08,730
With you protecting me in the dark,

381
00:21:08,730 --> 00:21:10,820
I have nothing to fear.

382
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:18,060
Xie Yun, don’t get hurt,

383
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:19,180
or I’ll feed you to sharks,

384
00:21:19,180 --> 00:21:21,300
alive or dead.

385
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:24,250
Fei,

386
00:21:24,250 --> 00:21:26,820
one lapse can lead to death.

387
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:29,010
I’m depending on you.

388
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,590
How could you?

389
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:49,710
We had a deal

390
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:51,200
that if I wrote down the poem,

391
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,710
you’d let me go.

392
00:21:52,710 --> 00:21:54,320
How could you go back on your word?

393
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:56,590
You sure can talk.

394
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:58,320
Let me

395
00:21:58,320 --> 00:22:00,280
stitch your lips together.

396
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:02,990
Tianying, hurry up.

397
00:22:02,990 --> 00:22:04,680
We have more important things to do.

398
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,440
Shen Tianshu,

399
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,590
aren’t you ashamed

400
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:10,990
of bullying a girl?

401
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:17,320
Well,

402
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:18,710
blame yourself

403
00:22:18,710 --> 00:22:21,560
for not being stupid enough.

404
00:22:28,350 --> 00:22:29,920
Lord Shen,

405
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,400
it’s been a while.

406
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,990
Xie Yun!

407
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:37,320
Are you ganging up

408
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:39,400
on a girl?

409
00:22:40,470 --> 00:22:42,510
Your Majesty,

410
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:45,350
what brings you here?

411
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:47,590
I heard that my naive cousin

412
00:22:47,590 --> 00:22:48,990
offended you,

413
00:22:48,990 --> 00:22:50,510
so I’m here to apologize.

414
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,560
Please be lenient

415
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:53,750
and let her go.

416
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:57,990
Why should I?

417
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,800
Don’t get me wrong.

418
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,110
I’m here to propose

419
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:06,680
a swap.

420
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,800
Take me instead of her.

421
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:11,560
Fair enough, isn’t it?

422
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:13,800
Now that you are here,

423
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:16,080
I can keep both of you.

424
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,510
You can.

425
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:24,320
But I’m afraid

426
00:23:24,320 --> 00:23:27,160
that’ll get you into trouble.

427
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,510
How so?

428
00:23:29,510 --> 00:23:30,510
Without Li Jinrong,

429
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:33,590
how could the rest of you

430
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:37,080
cause me trouble?

431
00:23:39,230 --> 00:23:41,230
We couldn’t

432
00:23:41,230 --> 00:23:43,110
if Gu Tianxian and his force

433
00:23:43,110 --> 00:23:44,590
were here

434
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:46,510
to help you.

435
00:23:47,230 --> 00:23:48,350
But too bad...

436
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,280
Report!

437
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:51,990
Lord Gu and his men

438
00:23:51,990 --> 00:23:53,750
are intercepted halfway.

439
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:04,830
Lord Gu is with one of my friends.

440
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:07,110
Yan is just

441
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:08,830
an ignorant girl.

442
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:10,280
Let her go

443
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:12,320
in exchange for your right-hand man.

444
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:15,110
You won’t say no

445
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:17,160
to such a great deal, will you?

446
00:24:18,990 --> 00:24:21,280
Why should I believe you?

447
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:23,590
You have eyes and ears
all over the Central Plains.

448
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:27,080
They’ll soon send the news to you.

449
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:28,870
If it’s not here

450
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:30,350
by midnight,

451
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:31,800
you can kill me.

452
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:36,080
Deal. You stay.

453
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:40,470
She can leave.

454
00:24:48,870 --> 00:24:50,160
Xie Yun.

455
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,800
Sorry for disturbing you.

456
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,590
Go. Don’t look back.

457
00:24:58,830 --> 00:24:59,870
Tianshu, you...

458
00:24:59,870 --> 00:25:02,510
Calm down, Tianying.

459
00:25:05,990 --> 00:25:07,960
He and I go way back.

460
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:10,400
Give us a minute.

461
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,200
I’ll explain everything to you later.

