also quit?

581
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:06,990
Didn’t Wang Lin tell you that?

582
00:32:21,110 --> 00:32:23,560
I was too busy practicing skills

583
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:25,710
to come out.

584
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:26,960
I didn’t realize until now

585
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:30,560
how different

586
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,590
the younger generation is.

587
00:32:34,870 --> 00:32:36,920
I’m flattered.

588
00:32:39,630 --> 00:32:40,960
Zhou Yitang,

589
00:32:44,560 --> 00:32:47,870
it took us three months of siege,

590
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:50,200
ten days of attacks to take this city

591
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:52,080
at the loss of half of our men.

592
00:32:52,710 --> 00:32:54,200
Yet here you are,
Wang Lin’s beloved disciple,

593
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:57,440
sitting here bossing others around.

594
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,960
I make the rules

595
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:00,800
on the battlefield.

596
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:02,110
Those are your own rules.

597
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:07,870
Why did you kill the captives?

598
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:09,230
We risked our lives

599
00:33:09,230 --> 00:33:11,750
to win this city

600
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:14,630
and we deserve to enjoy ourselves.

601
00:33:14,630 --> 00:33:16,110
Or why should we serve you?

602
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:18,320
We’re the ones

603
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:20,080
fighting on the battlefield
for Wang Lin.

604
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:23,200
If there are

605
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,710
so many rules to follow,

606
00:33:25,710 --> 00:33:27,680
I might as well quit.

607
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,560
Let’s go

608
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:32,510
if you’d like to join me.

609
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:33,630
Let’s go.

610
00:33:33,630 --> 00:33:34,680
Hold on.

611
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,960
That’s it? You’re leaving?

612
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:42,510
Fine.

613
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:46,040
I’ll give you something

614
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:49,920
to show Wang Lin.

615
00:34:01,870 --> 00:34:02,830
Leader!

616
00:34:09,470 --> 00:34:10,590
No wonder

617
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:13,350
you attempted to kill
Lord Gantang over and over.

618
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:17,990
He didn’t deserve to be the commander.

619
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:22,470
So by your logic,

620
00:34:23,830 --> 00:34:25,160
the weak can only

621
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:27,830
blame themselves for being killed.

622
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:31,510
Do you remember

623
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:33,810
you were one of them

624
00:34:34,560 --> 00:34:37,110
when my father first found you?

625
00:34:43,160 --> 00:34:45,270
General Wang Lin told me

626
00:34:45,270 --> 00:34:47,350
that he established the Anping Army

627
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:49,630
to protect the masses

628
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,630
from harm.

629
00:34:51,630 --> 00:34:52,870
Mr. Zhou has followed in

630
00:34:53,200 --> 00:34:56,000
his footsteps in that regard.

631
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,870
That’s why I was asked

632
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:01,830
to bring this badge

633
00:35:01,830 --> 00:35:03,630
to him.

634
00:35:12,350 --> 00:35:13,680
<i>Anping Army</i>
Turns out,

635
00:35:13,680 --> 00:35:17,520
I made the right choice.

636
00:35:17,520 --> 00:35:22,110
Since then, the Xiaos
have run out of their luck

637
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:25,720
and the Anping Army has fallen apart.

638
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:29,200
Once I open
the Color of Ocean and Heaven,

639
00:35:29,200 --> 00:35:30,630
I’ll build my own force

640
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:33,830
100 times stronger than Anping

641
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:39,790
and crush Zhou Yitang.

642
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,240
My lord,

643
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:52,240
it’s been confirmed that
Lord Gu and his men

644
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:53,440
were ambushed on the way here

645
00:35:53,440 --> 00:35:55,720
by the Route Gang and Yuyi Troupe.

646
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:56,590
I see.

647
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,920
Lord Shen,

648
00:36:01,630 --> 00:36:03,830
