668
00:38:31,270 --> 00:38:33,160
Looks like your help

669
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:35,920
didn’t come as expected.

670
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:38,960
Lord Shen,

671
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:41,200
